notes: India's lowest total for a completed innings v Zimbabwe
The last three wickets in India's innings fell on consecutive balls
After a rain delay between innings, Zimbabwe were set a revised target of 171 in 34 overs. Play was extended by an hour
Zimbabwe's 1st ever win against India in One-day Internationals. The only Test teams Zimbabwe are yet to beat in ODIs are West Indies and South Africa
